    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the definitive 'time capsule' specimen for the discerning collector. The exterior retains its original factory paint, showcasing a deep, mirror-like luster entirely free of swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings, preserved by a lifetime of climate-controlled storage and a recent professional-grade ceramic coating. Step inside to a cabin that remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery shows absolutely no bolster wear or creasing, the carpets are immaculate, and the interior still carries a faint hint of that distinct new-car aroma. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature\u2014from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been maintained with an open-checkbook policy at authorized service centers. The engine bay is detailed to a concours standard, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of inclement weather exposure. This sale includes the full documentation of its service history, the original window sticker, all sets of keys, and the factory-issued manuals. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless example that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did on the day of its original delivery.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
